The original comics have seen a resurgence of interest since the success of the films, with fans keen to explore more of the world that brought these iconic heroes to life in the first place. The Marvel Comics Luminart is an officially licensed Marvel Comics product, making it a great gift as well as the perfect piece of fan memorabilia.
